Table 19. Supplemental data for 68 large county governments
Note: Jurisdictions without data did not report for 1997.
a/ Population data are from the Bureau of the Census, July 1, 1997 county population estimates.
b/ "Total general expenditure" excludes utilities, county-operated liquor stores, and insurance trust benefits.
c/ "General functions only" full-time equivalent employment excludes utilities and county-operated liquor stores.
